}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "1244-01001068-51Z" and "1635" is silkscreened on the board. :Default settings are per the [https://fccid.io/document.php?id=3203567 FCC label] and [https://fccid.io/document.php?id=3203550 FCC images].
===Specifications=== *CPU: 600MHz Quad-Core Processor, RAM: 128 MB *Wireless Standard: 802.11b/g/n 2.4GHz, 802.11a/n/ac 5GHz *Wireless Speed: 400 Mbps for 2.4GHz, 867 Mbps for 5GHz *Operation Mode: Access point/Universal repeater/Client *Wireless Security: 64/128 bit WEP, WPA-PSK/WPA2-PSK *WLAN Features: Wave2, MU-MIMO, WPS, WMM, :Wireless scheduling, Auto channel selection :Wireless output power management *Antenna: 2x 2.4GHz, 2x 5GHz internal antennas *Ports: 1x LAN GbE, 1x Micro USB (Power Bank) *Power: 12V/1A DC int., 5V/2.1A DC micro USB
